Package com.sixdimensions.wcm.cq.component.bindings

Component Bindings Provider API - allows developers to bind value providers to resource types.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ComponentBindingsProvider A component bindings provider for every script load (including scripts in languages besides JSP).
ComponentBindingsProviderFactory A factory for retrieving component bindings provider.
CQVariables Extends the Sling Bindings to make available all of the objects the <cq:defineObjects /> tag adds as well as the sling objects.
CQVariablesService A service for retrieving CQ Variables.
